<h2 class="text-center text-success">General Questions</h2>

<h2>1. What is PSN Bank?</h2>
   PSN Bank is an Digital Bank that provides a range of financial services, including banking, saving, and investing, all accessible through our secure online platform.

2. Is PSN Bank a legitimate bank?
   Yes, PSN Bank is a legitimate and regulated financial institution. We are fully licensed to offer online banking services and follow all necessary regulations and security standards.

3. How do I get started with PSN Bank?
   To get started, visit our website and follow the instructions to create an account. You can then access your account and manage your finances online.

4. Is my money safe with PSN Bank?
   Absolutely. We take security seriously and use advanced encryption and authentication methods to protect your information. Your deposits are also insured up to a certain amount by [relevant insurance authority].

