5. How do I open an account with PSN Bank?
   Opening an account is simple. Visit our website, provide the required information, and follow the prompts to create an account.

6. Can I have multiple accounts with PSN Bank?
   Yes, you can have multiple accounts with us. Whether you need a checking account, savings account, or other specialized accounts, we offer a variety of options.

7. How can I access my accounts?
   You can access your accounts 24/7 through our online banking portal or our mobile app. Just log in using your credentials to manage your finances.

8. What do I do if I forget my password?
   If you forget your password, you can use the "Forgot Password" option on the login page to reset it securely.

