9. How do I transfer funds to another account?
   To transfer funds, log in to your account, navigate to the transfer section, and follow the prompts to initiate the transfer. You'll need the recipient's account details.

10. Are there any fees for online transactions?
    Some transactions may have associated fees. You can find details about our fees on our website or by contacting our customer support.

11. How long does it take for a transfer to be completed?
    Transfer times can vary depending on the type of transfer and the receiving bank. Many transfers are completed within a few business days.

