12. How secure is my personal and financial information?
    We use state-of-the-art encryption and security protocols to safeguard your data. Additionally, we regularly monitor accounts for any suspicious activity.

13. What should I do if I suspect fraudulent activity on my account?
    If you suspect any fraudulent activity, contact our customer support immediately. We will guide you through the necessary steps to secure your account.

14. Can I enable two-factor authentication for my account?
    Yes, we offer two-factor authentication as an added layer of security for your account. You can enable it in your account settings.

